This paper describes a method for improving visual search performance using visual attention mechanisms on a mobile robot. The paper focuses on the integration of three distinct mechanisms of visual attention, which are relevant to the fields of robotics, computer vision, artificial intelligence, machine learning, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
